<br>
Here is my understanding of the Chr issue...<br>
<br>
As said Chr is involved with Charming. The largest variable in charming is level difference. The high levels (50+ mainly) will see little impact of Chr compared to the lower levels (45- mainly).  This is because the Chr bonus is a fixed bonus but the level difference is not (higher levels get a larger spread of blue/green mobs). <br>
<br>
Using arbitrary numbers to demonstrate the idea: player level 30 is charming a blue (upto 3 levels below) while player level 50 is charming a blue (upto 7 levels below). The bonus of a Chr being the same, the 30 level needs more Chr than the 50 level due to charming further beneath their level. However, both should demonstrate the same need of Chr for charming white mobs (same level).<br>
